## Session close (explicit invoke only)

When the user says 收尾 / wrap up / `@session-close` / `/session-close`:

- Default **inline** reflection: answer Q1/Q2 in reasoning, show ≤3-line digest, single turn.
- Full Q1/Q2 go in `.session-close/handoffs/` handoff file.
- Append every file change to `.session-close/update-log.md`.
- Do **not** auto-prompt for session-close at end of unrelated turns.
